             were indicted for <rs id="t17830723-109-off497" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830723-109-off497" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-109-off497" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17830723-109-cd498" type="crimeDate">5th day of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-109-off497 t17830723-109-cd498"></join> last, one gelding, value 10 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17830723-109-victim1052" type="victimName">
                  Tomlinson 
                  Parkinson
               <interp inst="t17830723-109-victim1052" type="surname" value="Parkinson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-109-victim1052" type="given" value="Tomlinson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-109-victim1052" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-109-off497 t17830723-109-victim1052"></join>
